      • onBodyStart

        @Nullable
nu.xom.Element onBodyStart(nu.xom.Element body)
        Called upon creation of the XHTML body element. If the function returns an element, then the returned element becomes the new parent of any subsequently generated elements (effectively becoming the "container" for the generated document).
        Parameters:
        body - The XHTML body element
        Returns:
        The element that will be used as the container for the generated document
